def calculate_max_students(T, test_cases):
    results = []
    for case in test_cases:
        (N, B) = case
        l = B
        a = min(l)
        s = 1
        for x in range(len(l)):
            l[x] = l[x] - 2
            s += l[x]
        results.append((a - 1, s + len(l)))
    return results
